WEBVTT

00:01:35.519 --> 00:01:36.719
Leaving so soon?

00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:37.840
Weiguo.

00:01:38.280 --> 00:01:39.480
What brings you here?

00:01:40.719 --> 00:01:41.560
If there's anything,

00:01:41.560 --> 00:01:42.519
let's go inside to talk.

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:43.840
We'll go together later.

00:01:43.959 --> 00:01:44.359
Okay.

00:01:44.359 --> 00:01:45.439
Come on, inside, inside.

00:01:45.680 --> 00:01:46.239
Senior.

00:01:46.319 --> 00:01:47.760
I found you a large conference room.

00:01:48.719 --> 00:01:49.760
Why is he here?

00:01:50.599 --> 00:01:51.680
How should I know?

00:01:52.200 --> 00:01:53.000
Let's go see first.

00:01:54.120 --> 00:01:55.599
Why are you leaving?

00:01:57.239 --> 00:01:58.760
Wang Chunsheng and Li Lianbao.

00:01:59.079 --> 00:02:01.200
I'd call them the Super-Macho Twin Stars.

00:02:01.200 --> 00:02:03.200
Humanoid low-boiling-point nitroglycerin.

00:02:03.200 --> 00:02:06.719
Explodes when cold, hot, hit, or near a flame.

00:02:06.719 --> 00:02:08.240
Tong Qiu can trigger it.

00:02:08.240 --> 00:02:10.280
The Unlucky Human Trio's combined attack.

00:02:10.280 --> 00:02:11.360
As for those two,

00:02:11.360 --> 00:02:12.479
we still have to help.

00:02:12.479 --> 00:02:13.360
It's just that

00:02:13.360 --> 00:02:14.879
there should be a small price, right?

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:23.680
Hello?

00:02:24.520 --> 00:02:25.560
Third Uncle, I'm here.

00:02:25.560 --> 00:02:26.479
Which table are you at?

00:02:26.479 --> 00:02:27.280
Walk further in.

00:02:27.400 --> 00:02:28.280
I see you.

00:02:43.840 --> 00:02:45.280
Why aren't you out having fun this weekend?

00:02:45.280 --> 00:02:46.240
What did you come to see me for?

00:02:50.520 --> 00:02:51.240
Third Uncle.

00:02:51.680 --> 00:02:53.759
With this thing happening at home now,

00:02:54.199 --> 00:02:55.800
how could I be in the mood to go out?

00:03:00.240 --> 00:03:01.039
Um...

00:03:01.479 --> 00:03:02.439
This time,

00:03:03.039 --> 00:03:05.919
Third Uncle, you really don't plan to help my dad?

00:03:10.960 --> 00:03:11.840
I think...

00:03:12.240 --> 00:03:13.800
I also heard

00:03:14.520 --> 00:03:16.719
that my dad once

00:03:16.960 --> 00:03:19.199
went to jail for you, right?

00:03:19.639 --> 00:03:22.400
So how can you bear to see him go in again?

00:03:25.560 --> 00:03:27.000
With your dad's temper,

00:03:27.319 --> 00:03:28.479
always ready to hit someone,

00:03:28.479 --> 00:03:29.560
he's bound to get in trouble sooner or later.

00:03:29.560 --> 00:03:30.800
He deserves to learn a lesson.

00:03:31.520 --> 00:03:32.560
Besides,

00:03:32.840 --> 00:03:35.719
wouldn't it be better for you if he's inside?

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:36.879
No one would be on your case then.

00:03:41.120 --> 00:03:42.439
That guy...

00:03:43.199 --> 00:03:43.960
It's true.

00:03:44.319 --> 00:03:46.400
He has a bad temper and lots of flaws.

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:47.199
And he's super lazy.

00:03:47.199 --> 00:03:48.719
But no matter what, I think

00:03:49.159 --> 00:03:50.639
he's still my dad after all.

00:03:51.639 --> 00:03:53.840
And this time I was there, Third Uncle.

00:03:53.840 --> 00:03:55.159
I saw with my own eyes that it was that

00:03:55.159 --> 00:03:56.759
Tang Zhixin who started it.

00:03:56.919 --> 00:03:57.960
If it were me, I'd...

00:03:58.479 --> 00:03:59.719
I'd have to hit him too.

00:03:59.840 --> 00:04:01.520
Isn't your Second Uncle handling it?

00:04:01.680 --> 00:04:03.479
We just wait for his news, okay?

00:04:03.479 --> 00:04:04.639
Second Uncle, he...

00:04:04.639 --> 00:04:06.199
He just found a lawyer,

00:04:06.199 --> 00:04:08.360
but he didn't sound very committed on the phone.

00:04:09.960 --> 00:04:10.719
Third Uncle...

00:04:11.280 --> 00:04:12.280
Please.

00:04:15.960 --> 00:04:16.839
Don't worry.

00:04:17.199 --> 00:04:18.120
It's all arranged.

00:04:19.600 --> 00:04:21.160
Wang Chunsheng is my older male cousin.

00:04:21.160 --> 00:04:22.560
My eldest aunt's son.

00:04:22.560 --> 00:04:24.040
This is my older sister-in-law.

00:04:24.040 --> 00:04:25.319
She takes good care of me.

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:26.680
And this young man here

00:04:26.680 --> 00:04:27.439
is my nephew.

00:04:27.439 --> 00:04:28.160
His name is Wang Fei.

00:04:28.160 --> 00:04:29.360
Sit properly. Greet him.

00:04:30.079 --> 00:04:30.839
Hello, Uncle.

00:04:31.360 --> 00:04:31.839
Well...

00:04:37.720 --> 00:04:39.480
Had I known about this connection earlier,

00:04:39.480 --> 00:04:41.600
we wouldn't have needed all this trouble, right?

00:04:42.079 --> 00:04:42.800
Da Zhang.

00:04:43.040 --> 00:04:45.040
I'm not here to poach your case.

00:04:45.920 --> 00:04:49.199
If there's any difficulty with this matter,

00:04:49.199 --> 00:04:51.839
Come on, Senior, don't embarrass me.

00:04:51.839 --> 00:04:52.959
If I had to trouble you with this,

00:04:52.959 --> 00:04:54.839
I'd lose all face.

00:04:57.240 --> 00:04:58.920
Show them this.

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:00.519
Maybe they'll give up.

00:05:03.720 --> 00:05:05.399
This is my father's draft from back then.

00:05:05.839 --> 00:05:07.920
It's a declaration jointly signed

00:05:07.920 --> 00:05:10.040
by my youngest aunt and my grandfather.

00:05:10.079 --> 00:05:11.160
It's been notarized.

00:05:11.360 --> 00:05:12.920
It clearly states

00:05:12.920 --> 00:05:14.560
that my father and my youngest aunt

00:05:14.560 --> 00:05:16.920
renounce their inheritance rights to Pengle Xuan.

00:05:17.199 --> 00:05:18.319
As a keepsake,

00:05:18.319 --> 00:05:19.439
I've kept it all this time.

00:05:19.639 --> 00:05:21.680
Weiguo, this is impressive.

00:05:21.680 --> 00:05:22.439
Second Brother.

00:05:22.439 --> 00:05:24.680
There really was such a declaration back then.

00:05:24.680 --> 00:05:26.920
Your eldest brother and I didn't take it seriously.

00:05:27.199 --> 00:05:29.639
We kept moving it around and lost it.

00:05:34.240 --> 00:05:34.759
Hold on.

00:05:34.879 --> 00:05:35.560
You had this?

00:05:35.560 --> 00:05:36.560
Why didn't you bring it out sooner?

00:05:36.560 --> 00:05:38.279
I tried to give it to Eldest Brother the day after I returned.

00:05:38.279 --> 00:05:39.079
But he refused it.

00:05:39.079 --> 00:05:39.959
What could I do?

00:05:43.480 --> 00:05:44.160
Eldest Brother.

00:05:44.879 --> 00:05:45.680
And this too.

00:05:46.279 --> 00:05:47.560
It's very important to you.

00:05:48.079 --> 00:05:48.879
Take it.

00:05:48.959 --> 00:05:50.120
You giving me this thing,

00:05:50.839 --> 00:05:52.720
no matter how important it is to me,

00:05:53.040 --> 00:05:54.319
I don't want it.

00:05:58.120 --> 00:05:59.319
This Tang Zhixin,

00:05:59.319 --> 00:06:00.439
once he realizes

00:06:00.439 --> 00:06:02.040
he can't gain any advantage at Pengle Xuan,

00:06:02.040 --> 00:06:03.160
he'll give up.

00:06:03.519 --> 00:06:05.199
As for the beating he took,

00:06:05.319 --> 00:06:07.040
we'll compensate as required.

00:06:08.759 --> 00:06:10.120
So you can rest assured.

00:06:10.560 --> 00:06:11.360
Thank you.

00:06:11.360 --> 00:06:12.439
No problem, no problem.

00:06:19.639 --> 00:06:20.720
Manager Li, leave this matter to me.

00:06:20.720 --> 00:06:21.680
You can rest easy.

00:06:21.680 --> 00:06:23.720
Attorney Zhang, I appreciate the sentiment.

00:06:23.720 --> 00:06:25.279
But you must accept the fee.

00:06:25.560 --> 00:06:26.319
No, Manager Li.

00:06:26.319 --> 00:06:27.399
Don't put me in a difficult position.

00:06:27.399 --> 00:06:29.199
My senior is a partner at Daheng.

00:06:29.199 --> 00:06:30.240
It's not appropriate.

00:06:30.240 --> 00:06:31.480
I'm not joking.

00:06:31.480 --> 00:06:32.959
Rice is a major client.

00:06:32.959 --> 00:06:34.399
My senior being able to help me

00:06:34.399 --> 00:06:36.000
is a huge advantage for me.

00:06:36.560 --> 00:06:37.199
Manager Li.

00:06:38.040 --> 00:06:39.600
I'll need to work with you in the future.

00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:40.680
Please look out for me.

00:06:41.079 --> 00:06:42.319
Okay, okay, of course, of course.

00:06:42.319 --> 00:06:43.199
Then let's schedule another time.

00:06:43.199 --> 00:06:44.160
Sure, sure.

00:06:44.160 --> 00:06:45.000
Alright.

00:06:50.439 --> 00:06:52.639
Why is Ma Weiguo everywhere?

00:06:58.199 --> 00:06:59.879
Hello? What is it?

00:07:00.639 --> 00:07:02.839
I want to start immigration procedures for Jenny.

00:07:03.120 --> 00:07:04.720
I need you to sign a consent form.

00:07:04.720 --> 00:07:05.600
Immigration?

00:07:05.839 --> 00:07:07.079
Immigrate where?

00:07:25.439 --> 00:07:26.120
Hu Nana

00:07:26.480 --> 00:07:27.639
What do you want?

00:07:28.199 --> 00:07:29.560
You and Lao Kai want to emigrate.

00:07:29.560 --> 00:07:31.279
I don't care if you move to Mars.

00:07:31.519 --> 00:07:32.560
Yuanyuan is so young.

00:07:32.560 --> 00:07:33.519
Why go abroad?

00:07:33.759 --> 00:07:35.560
I'm telling you, I don't agree.

00:07:35.560 --> 00:07:37.040
Li Lianbao, you don't have to be like this with me.

00:07:37.199 --> 00:07:38.959
Emigrating is a simple matter.

00:07:39.120 --> 00:07:41.439
I just want our child to get a better education.

00:07:41.639 --> 00:07:42.759
Now there's an opportunity.

00:07:42.759 --> 00:07:43.800
And we have the means.

00:07:43.800 --> 00:07:45.560
Isn't China's basic education better?

00:07:45.639 --> 00:07:47.199
You can emigrate later if you want.

00:07:47.199 --> 00:07:48.720
The earlier she goes, the sooner she adapts.

00:07:49.040 --> 00:07:50.920
Yuanyuan is studying piano.

00:07:51.279 --> 00:07:52.959
Of course you should study Western music abroad.

00:07:52.959 --> 00:07:53.560
Enough!

00:07:53.720 --> 00:07:55.240
Don't give me all that nonsense.

00:07:55.439 --> 00:07:56.560
Let me make this clear to you.

00:07:57.120 --> 00:07:58.519
If you want to take my daughter to emigrate...

00:07:58.639 --> 00:07:59.720
...forget about it.

00:08:00.240 --> 00:08:00.959
How about this?

00:08:01.120 --> 00:08:02.839
Give me custody of Yuanyuan.

00:08:03.319 --> 00:08:04.600
Don't even think about that either.

00:08:06.639 --> 00:08:07.720
Hello, Tom.

00:08:08.720 --> 00:08:09.480
Lao Kai.

00:08:09.920 --> 00:08:12.399
Was emigrating your idea?

00:08:12.720 --> 00:08:14.160
Watch your tone.

00:08:14.600 --> 00:08:16.360
It's fine, it's fine.

00:08:17.959 --> 00:08:20.040
Tom, calm down.

00:08:20.279 --> 00:08:21.600
We really just want...

00:08:21.600 --> 00:08:23.199
...to give Jenny a better life.

00:08:23.720 --> 00:08:24.720
Don't worry.

00:08:24.959 --> 00:08:26.240
I can provide all that.

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:29.480
I know it's hard to find a job now.

00:08:29.920 --> 00:08:31.519
If money is tight...

00:08:31.519 --> 00:08:33.000
...you don't have to pay this anymore.

00:08:34.200 --> 00:08:35.279
Stop pretending to be so noble.

00:08:36.039 --> 00:08:37.039
I'm doing just fine.

00:08:37.039 --> 00:08:38.120
I don't need your pity.

00:08:38.679 --> 00:08:40.480
And don't try to look good in front of my daughter.

00:08:40.559 --> 00:08:42.240
I won't spend a single cent of yours.

00:08:42.399 --> 00:08:43.799
I'll earn money to support her for life.

00:08:43.919 --> 00:08:45.559
Tom, you've really misunderstood.

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:48.600
We don't want to fight with you over anything.

00:08:49.000 --> 00:08:50.960
We're purely doing this for Jenny.

00:08:51.519 --> 00:08:53.039
Isn't Martin your good friend?

00:08:53.039 --> 00:08:53.960
He's doing very well now.

00:08:53.960 --> 00:08:54.559
Isn't it precisely because...

00:08:54.559 --> 00:08:55.759
Don't mention him to me!

00:08:56.200 --> 00:08:57.679
I'll say it one last time.

00:08:58.080 --> 00:09:00.840
If you want to take my daughter to emigrate, no way!

00:09:04.720 --> 00:09:05.559
You're insane.

00:09:07.279 --> 00:09:09.399
Nana, Nana!

00:09:33.720 --> 00:09:36.559
Old Tong, you're finally here!

00:09:36.559 --> 00:09:38.519
I've been waiting and waiting...

00:09:38.519 --> 00:09:39.840
...for you to arrive.

00:09:40.120 --> 00:09:41.240
Now that you're here...

00:09:41.320 --> 00:09:43.799
...you must share your experience.

00:09:44.039 --> 00:09:44.919
You're too kind.

00:09:44.919 --> 00:09:47.639
I'm here mainly to learn.

00:09:48.080 --> 00:09:50.960
So modest. You can tell you're from the city.

00:09:51.399 --> 00:09:54.440
But excessive modesty is just pride.

00:09:55.159 --> 00:09:57.000
Yes, yes, I... I...

00:09:57.360 --> 00:09:58.240
Right, right.

00:09:58.240 --> 00:09:58.960
Old Tong...

00:09:58.960 --> 00:10:00.519
...our place here is newly established.

00:10:00.679 --> 00:10:02.840
Many are newly hired staff.

00:10:02.840 --> 00:10:04.279
Their professional skills...

00:10:04.799 --> 00:10:06.039
...leave a lot to be desired.

00:10:06.519 --> 00:10:07.440
Since you're here...

00:10:07.440 --> 00:10:09.600
...how about you handle the job training?

00:10:09.759 --> 00:10:11.159
I'm new here.

00:10:11.159 --> 00:10:12.919
I'll follow your arrangements.

00:10:12.919 --> 00:10:14.240
Great, great, great.

00:10:15.080 --> 00:10:16.000
Old Tong...

00:10:16.360 --> 00:10:19.320
...our location is really too remote.

00:10:20.120 --> 00:10:21.440
And the people are too honest.

00:10:21.960 --> 00:10:23.360
I won't beat around the bush.

00:10:23.480 --> 00:10:25.600
Show us some real skill.

00:10:25.600 --> 00:10:26.600
Teach by word and example.

00:10:26.600 --> 00:10:27.840
Say what's on your mind.

00:10:27.840 --> 00:10:29.399
Don't hold back at all.

00:10:36.279 --> 00:10:37.000
Answer the phone.

00:10:37.000 --> 00:10:37.799
I'll step out.

00:10:37.799 --> 00:10:38.600
No, no, no.

00:10:38.600 --> 00:10:39.960
This is your, your, your office.

00:10:39.960 --> 00:10:41.240
I'll, I'll go out.

00:10:45.559 --> 00:10:47.000
Honey, you finally called!

00:10:47.000 --> 00:10:48.120
I've missed you so much.

00:10:49.000 --> 00:10:51.120
I want to come back in a couple of days.

00:10:52.360 --> 00:10:53.679
You forgive me?

00:10:53.679 --> 00:10:54.919
Who said I forgive you?

00:10:55.120 --> 00:10:56.440
I'm still angry.

00:10:58.840 --> 00:11:01.519
But... it's my ovulation period.

00:11:03.519 --> 00:11:05.720
It's understandable for a wife to be angry.

00:11:05.720 --> 00:11:06.679
It's only right.

00:11:06.879 --> 00:11:08.200
My wife is considerate of the bigger picture...

00:11:08.200 --> 00:11:10.320
...and that's why she's giving me some face.

00:11:10.480 --> 00:11:11.679
You know what's good for you.

00:11:21.080 --> 00:11:22.399
Where are you now?

00:11:22.399 --> 00:11:23.480
I'm at the bank.

00:11:24.120 --> 00:11:26.039
Why do I hear a rooster crowing?

00:11:28.080 --> 00:11:30.000
A colleague changed their ringtone.

00:11:30.000 --> 00:11:32.200
Isn't that, isn't that funny?

00:11:40.559 --> 00:11:42.279
Honey, maybe... maybe you shouldn't come.

00:11:42.279 --> 00:11:43.120
It's too much trouble for you.

00:11:43.120 --> 00:11:44.639
I'll come to Xi'an to see you.

00:11:45.840 --> 00:11:46.919
Alright.

00:11:47.159 --> 00:11:48.360
Then come as soon as possible.

00:11:48.720 --> 00:11:51.320
Okay, I'll go as soon as I finish up here in a couple of days.

00:11:58.759 --> 00:12:00.320
Darn it, what is this?

00:12:24.399 --> 00:12:25.039
Brother Liu.

00:12:25.320 --> 00:12:26.480
I need a favor.

00:12:26.799 --> 00:12:28.480
That Booker Restaurant case.

00:12:28.480 --> 00:12:30.360
Help me find out which team did it.

00:12:30.600 --> 00:12:31.679
Let me know if you hear anything.

00:12:32.039 --> 00:12:33.159
Keep this confidential.

00:12:33.159 --> 00:12:34.200
Don't let anyone know.

00:12:34.639 --> 00:12:35.360
That's it.

00:12:35.879 --> 00:12:36.559
Bye.

00:12:38.399 --> 00:12:39.360
What's so funny?

00:12:40.320 --> 00:12:41.559
You scared me.

00:12:43.159 --> 00:12:44.039
Listen.

00:12:44.360 --> 00:12:45.519
I've figured it out.

00:12:46.000 --> 00:12:47.960
Why am I even looking for a job?

00:12:47.960 --> 00:12:50.279
Aren't they all saying I'm too old and expensive?

00:12:50.360 --> 00:12:52.159
Fine. I won't serve them anymore.

00:12:52.159 --> 00:12:53.120
I'll do my own thing.

00:12:53.679 --> 00:12:55.480
You're starting a business?

00:12:56.480 --> 00:12:58.720
Well, how about this then?

00:12:58.720 --> 00:13:01.120
While you're at it, tell my mom.

00:13:01.120 --> 00:13:02.679
Say you need help for your startup.

00:13:02.679 --> 00:13:03.519
Let me join in.

00:13:03.519 --> 00:13:04.919
I'm short on cash lately anyway.

00:13:05.399 --> 00:13:07.600
No, if you're short on money,

00:13:07.600 --> 00:13:08.519
just tell me.

00:13:08.519 --> 00:13:09.519
I have some here.

00:13:09.679 --> 00:13:10.679
But my situation...

00:13:10.679 --> 00:13:12.320
You really can't help with.

00:13:12.320 --> 00:13:14.039
Just focus on preparing your photo exhibition.

00:13:14.039 --> 00:13:15.720
How could I possibly take your money?

00:13:15.720 --> 00:13:17.919
I know the principle of being indebted.

00:13:18.039 --> 00:13:19.480
Alright, go home and rest early.

00:13:19.480 --> 00:13:20.440
Don't rush off.

00:13:21.360 --> 00:13:22.960
I have a surprise for you.

00:13:27.519 --> 00:13:29.399
You've really taken a lot of photos.

00:13:30.639 --> 00:13:33.159
I want the theme to be Beijing's twenty-year transformation.

00:13:33.159 --> 00:13:34.000
Specifically?

00:13:34.000 --> 00:13:36.279
Start with the familiar Baofang Hutong.

00:13:37.279 --> 00:13:38.639
Sounds interesting.

00:13:39.960 --> 00:13:41.440
How do you want me to help?

00:13:43.200 --> 00:13:45.480
I want to use you four brothers as a thread.

00:13:45.600 --> 00:13:47.720
Take a set of before-and-after photos.

00:13:48.080 --> 00:13:50.200
I'll also collect some old items.

00:13:50.200 --> 00:13:51.120
Old photos.

00:13:51.120 --> 00:13:52.320
And some of your old...

00:13:52.320 --> 00:13:54.039
food, things you used, clothes you wore.

00:13:54.480 --> 00:13:56.440
Then I hope you'll recreate them...

00:13:56.440 --> 00:13:57.399
in your present state.

00:13:59.840 --> 00:14:01.399
I just remembered something I need to do.

00:14:01.399 --> 00:14:02.320
I have to go.

00:14:02.320 --> 00:14:03.600
Uncle, don't go!

00:14:03.759 --> 00:14:05.720
I was counting on you to lead this for me.

00:14:06.159 --> 00:14:08.679
You should go to your mom for this.

00:14:09.360 --> 00:14:11.000
What good would finding my mom do?

00:14:11.320 --> 00:14:13.320
I thought Uncle Ma was quite concerned...

00:14:13.320 --> 00:14:14.519
about Uncle Wang's situation.

00:14:14.600 --> 00:14:16.440
I thought you four had made up.

00:14:16.559 --> 00:14:18.679
Made up? Made up my ass!

00:14:18.799 --> 00:14:20.519
He's just showing off.

00:14:20.720 --> 00:14:22.360
Making us shamelessly apologize.

00:14:22.360 --> 00:14:23.360
And suck up to him.

00:14:31.080 --> 00:14:32.799
That's pretty wild.

00:14:32.960 --> 00:14:33.639
Who is it?

00:14:34.080 --> 00:14:35.360
You don't know him.

00:14:36.000 --> 00:14:37.759
I'm not that conservative.

00:14:38.039 --> 00:14:39.919
Your uncle loved to have fun when he was young too.

00:14:40.080 --> 00:14:41.440
But a reminder, Tongtong.

00:14:41.440 --> 00:14:42.879
As a girl, you still need to be careful.

00:14:42.879 --> 00:14:44.919
What are you talking about? You're overthinking.

00:14:44.919 --> 00:14:46.200
Go, go, go!

00:14:46.200 --> 00:14:46.639
No.

00:14:47.720 --> 00:14:49.759
I think he looks familiar.

00:14:50.080 --> 00:14:51.480
Why would a foreigner look familiar?

00:14:51.480 --> 00:14:51.960
Go on, get out.

00:14:51.960 --> 00:14:52.440
A foreigner?

00:14:52.440 --> 00:14:54.000
With a foreigner, you need to be even more careful!

00:14:54.080 --> 00:14:55.279
What nonsense are you saying?

00:14:55.279 --> 00:14:56.720
Young lady, don't play so recklessly.

00:14:56.720 --> 00:14:57.840
You're overthinking it.

00:14:58.519 --> 00:14:59.759
What?

00:15:35.960 --> 00:15:36.799
Big brother.

00:15:37.000 --> 00:15:38.759
Stop fussing, sit down.

00:15:41.759 --> 00:15:43.679
Qiu'er, why are you so listless today?

00:15:43.679 --> 00:15:46.600
You get the brothers started eating and drinking.

00:15:48.279 --> 00:15:49.440
Wait, there's one more dish.

00:15:50.519 --> 00:15:53.200
Big brother, there's something...

00:15:53.200 --> 00:15:54.320
I need to discuss with you.

00:15:54.320 --> 00:15:55.279
Not now, Second Brother.

00:15:56.039 --> 00:15:57.320
We'll talk later.

00:16:00.000 --> 00:16:00.519
Here.

00:16:00.519 --> 00:16:01.240
Here.

00:16:04.120 --> 00:16:07.519
I have a good idea in my heart.

00:16:09.320 --> 00:16:10.279
So here's the thing.

00:16:10.879 --> 00:16:11.840
This...

00:16:13.159 --> 00:16:14.919
I won't say much more.

00:16:15.720 --> 00:16:17.000
It's all in this drink.

00:16:19.320 --> 00:16:21.200
Weiguo.

00:16:22.600 --> 00:16:23.519
I'll finish this.

00:16:23.519 --> 00:16:24.039
To keep you company.

00:16:24.039 --> 00:16:25.320
Come on, come on.

00:16:25.480 --> 00:16:26.919
Big brother, you don't need to drink.

00:16:27.600 --> 00:16:28.840
There's no need for thanks between us.

00:16:29.519 --> 00:16:30.480
No, no, no.

00:16:30.720 --> 00:16:31.480
Sit down.

00:16:33.759 --> 00:16:34.840
I don't need your thanks.

00:16:36.519 --> 00:16:37.960
Hey, Ma Weiguo.

00:16:38.320 --> 00:16:40.519
Is it fun always being a Monday morning quarterback?

00:16:40.960 --> 00:16:42.799
Does big brother need to thank you?

00:16:43.200 --> 00:16:44.440
If you had produced that IOU earlier,

00:16:44.440 --> 00:16:46.360
would big brother have had to suffer like that?

00:16:46.879 --> 00:16:47.559
Big brother.

00:16:48.519 --> 00:16:49.759
After all these years...

00:16:50.000 --> 00:16:51.360
how come you still haven't changed?

00:16:52.200 --> 00:16:53.200
How are you still so impulsive?

00:16:53.200 --> 00:16:54.080
So unreasonable?

00:16:58.879 --> 00:16:59.639
Weiguo.

00:16:59.639 --> 00:17:01.200
You... the way you're talking...

00:17:01.200 --> 00:17:03.279
Look, we closed the shop specially today.

00:17:03.279 --> 00:17:04.960
Your big brother prepared this whole table of food.

00:17:04.960 --> 00:17:05.400
No, no, no.

00:17:05.400 --> 00:17:06.400
All just to thank you!

00:17:06.400 --> 00:17:07.799
I said I don't need his thanks.

00:17:12.680 --> 00:17:14.279
Fine. Perfect timing.

00:17:15.880 --> 00:17:17.319
Since we're being official about it,

00:17:17.519 --> 00:17:19.119
then let's go point by point.

00:17:19.640 --> 00:17:20.440
You say...

00:17:20.440 --> 00:17:22.039
I came back just to humiliate you?

00:17:22.319 --> 00:17:23.359
To disgrace you?

00:17:23.720 --> 00:17:24.960
Then my words still stand.

00:17:25.599 --> 00:17:27.240
The three of you owe me an apology.

00:17:27.359 --> 00:17:28.319
Pay up now.

00:17:33.079 --> 00:17:34.720
Are you out of your mind?

00:17:39.799 --> 00:17:41.119
You really are crazy.

00:17:45.480 --> 00:17:46.279
They've all left.

00:17:46.279 --> 00:17:46.960
You apologize.

00:17:51.079 --> 00:17:52.160
Apologize to yourself.

00:17:52.720 --> 00:17:54.720
Then, keep on making trouble.

00:17:55.319 --> 00:17:56.279
Good luck with that.

00:18:23.279 --> 00:18:25.079
So it was you who went to find him.

00:18:26.079 --> 00:18:28.039
No, why would I need you to beg him for me?

00:18:28.039 --> 00:18:29.640
What the heck does he think he is?

00:18:29.640 --> 00:18:32.759
Dad, Third Uncle is not the kind of person you think.

00:18:33.160 --> 00:18:34.599
Even if I didn't go to him,

00:18:34.599 --> 00:18:36.519
he wouldn't ignore your problem.

00:18:36.519 --> 00:18:37.559
Third Uncle also said

00:18:37.799 --> 00:18:39.599
he will take full responsibility for my issues.

00:18:39.599 --> 00:18:41.599
How is he going to take full responsibility for you?

00:18:42.000 --> 00:18:43.240
The school is about to expel you.

00:18:43.240 --> 00:18:44.720
Take full responsibility, my foot!

00:18:44.720 --> 00:18:45.440
What?

00:18:45.440 --> 00:18:46.720
Can he take care of you for the rest of your life?

00:18:46.720 --> 00:18:49.240
Make our Wang family ancestors proud from their graves?

00:18:49.240 --> 00:18:50.559
No, I have to go find him right now.

00:18:50.559 --> 00:18:52.200
Dad, Dad, don't go, don't.

00:18:52.200 --> 00:18:53.039
Get out of my way.

00:18:53.039 --> 00:18:56.079
Dad, during the time I've spent with him,

00:18:57.079 --> 00:18:58.880
I finally feel understood by someone.

00:19:00.039 --> 00:19:01.519
I'm willing to trust him.

00:19:03.400 --> 00:19:05.720
At least Third Uncle can understand what I'm saying.

00:19:06.359 --> 00:19:07.440
Not like with you.

00:19:07.440 --> 00:19:08.720
Talking is just exhausting.

00:19:09.160 --> 00:19:10.839
You always say you understand, you understand,

00:19:11.319 --> 00:19:12.799
but actually you don't understand anything.

00:19:12.960 --> 00:19:13.759
No, well, well...

00:19:13.759 --> 00:19:15.720
So your Third Uncle, he understands everything?

00:19:15.720 --> 00:19:17.160
Well, he's seen the world.

00:19:18.240 --> 00:19:20.400
What I understand or don't, he gets it all.

00:19:28.720 --> 00:19:30.519
You've only known him for a few days.

00:19:38.680 --> 00:19:40.400
Go back to your room and do your homework, now.

00:20:11.279 --> 00:20:12.039
You wanted to see me.

00:20:13.680 --> 00:20:14.759
I just want to ask you,

00:20:16.119 --> 00:20:18.200
are you sincere about wanting to help Feifei?

00:20:20.279 --> 00:20:21.200
The issue isn't about...

00:20:21.200 --> 00:20:21.680
No, no, no.

00:20:21.680 --> 00:20:23.160
Don't give me that useless talk.

00:20:26.480 --> 00:20:27.440
This child,

00:20:29.039 --> 00:20:30.559
now wants you to help him.

00:20:31.119 --> 00:20:32.799
I just want to know if you're sincere.

00:20:32.799 --> 00:20:34.119
I sincerely want to help him.

00:20:34.279 --> 00:20:35.400
But I have conditions.

00:20:35.400 --> 00:20:37.000
Isn't it just about making me apologize to you?

00:20:38.200 --> 00:20:39.160
For the child's sake,

00:20:39.720 --> 00:20:41.200
I'd even kneel to you.

00:20:41.799 --> 00:20:43.000
But don't mess with me, okay?

00:20:43.000 --> 00:20:43.960
Don't worry.

00:20:44.759 --> 00:20:45.720
He's my nephew.

00:20:45.720 --> 00:20:46.720
I won't harm him.

00:20:50.680 --> 00:20:51.920
Do you want to come take a look?

00:21:01.640 --> 00:21:02.559
Remember this, right?

00:21:06.039 --> 00:21:07.279
When you were little,

00:21:08.200 --> 00:21:11.799
you always waited here for your mom and dad to come home.

00:21:12.000 --> 00:21:14.680
You said standing here was high up, you could see far.

00:21:15.720 --> 00:21:16.400
Yeah.

00:21:16.640 --> 00:21:18.160
You could see the alley entrance at a glance.

00:21:18.599 --> 00:21:19.480
You could see Auntie Li

00:21:19.480 --> 00:21:21.400
carrying honey pastries and steamed buns.

00:21:21.519 --> 00:21:22.880
You two would both run up to her.

00:21:23.720 --> 00:21:25.519
Li Lianbao, on the other hand, would hide far away.

00:21:26.119 --> 00:21:28.119
You could see Uncle Tong in a suit,

00:21:28.119 --> 00:21:29.319
carrying a briefcase.

00:21:29.839 --> 00:21:31.200
There were always one or two books in it,

00:21:31.200 --> 00:21:32.160
by Jin Yong and Gu Long.

00:21:32.519 --> 00:21:34.559
You could also see Uncle Wang in a leather jacket,

00:21:35.200 --> 00:21:37.359
riding his Phoenix brand bicycle.

00:21:40.960 --> 00:21:42.039
You all said,

00:21:42.039 --> 00:21:43.640
my dad, my mom,

00:21:44.000 --> 00:21:45.480
would definitely come down this road too.

00:21:46.559 --> 00:21:47.839
I'll wait for them right here.

00:21:49.319 --> 00:21:50.440
Every single day I waited,

00:21:50.640 --> 00:21:51.880
I recorded it.

00:21:56.359 --> 00:21:57.000
Look.

00:21:58.119 --> 00:21:59.440
This is the last day.

00:22:11.200 --> 00:22:12.079
Don't think too much about it.

00:22:12.960 --> 00:22:15.160
Weiguo will need you to take care of him from now on.

00:22:15.400 --> 00:22:16.720
Pull yourself together.

00:22:17.799 --> 00:22:18.640
I know where he is.

00:22:18.640 --> 00:22:20.000
It was May of 1998.

00:22:20.400 --> 00:22:21.279
New York.

00:22:22.480 --> 00:22:24.079
That accident was in the papers.

00:22:25.160 --> 00:22:27.599
But their names were nowhere to be found in the article.

00:22:34.440 --> 00:22:35.519
To this day,

00:22:36.319 --> 00:22:38.000
I still don't know where they are.

00:22:38.759 --> 00:22:40.680
What they were talking about when they were alive,

00:22:41.160 --> 00:22:41.960
what they were doing.

00:22:50.240 --> 00:22:50.920
Big Brother.

00:22:51.680 --> 00:22:53.160
You ask me why I left.

00:22:53.720 --> 00:22:55.039
Because I'm too darn cowardly.

00:22:58.839 --> 00:22:59.759
All these years,

00:23:00.279 --> 00:23:01.519
I've both hated you all

00:23:02.640 --> 00:23:03.839
and felt I owed you.

00:23:07.559 --> 00:23:08.440
Ma Weiguo!

00:23:08.720 --> 00:23:09.599
Ma Weiguo!

00:23:09.599 --> 00:23:10.440
Ma Weiguo!

00:23:13.880 --> 00:23:15.160
Brought you some soda.

00:23:15.680 --> 00:23:16.400
Come down!

00:23:16.400 --> 00:23:17.200
Come on down.

00:23:18.400 --> 00:23:19.319
Come down!

00:23:19.440 --> 00:23:20.079
Down.

00:23:24.440 --> 00:23:27.920
Maybe we should just let this matter go.

00:23:28.359 --> 00:23:29.640
What are you all doing here?

00:23:31.039 --> 00:23:32.039
Feifei called us.

00:23:32.039 --> 00:23:33.200
Afraid you two would fight.

00:23:35.240 --> 00:23:36.519
Brother, Weiguo.

00:23:37.480 --> 00:23:38.359
Let me say one more thing.

00:23:38.359 --> 00:23:39.599
All these years, I feel

00:23:40.599 --> 00:23:42.480
we brothers have all had it pretty tough.

00:23:42.920 --> 00:23:45.680
Let's just turn the page on some things.

00:23:46.519 --> 00:23:49.279
As long as Big Brother agrees, I...

00:23:56.279 --> 00:23:56.680
What's wrong?

00:23:56.680 --> 00:23:58.119
Don't move. Turn your face away.

00:23:58.319 --> 00:23:58.960
What is it?

00:23:59.200 --> 00:23:59.960
Turn around.

00:24:02.680 --> 00:24:03.480
What are you doing?

00:24:04.839 --> 00:24:05.640
Ma Weiguo!

00:24:05.640 --> 00:24:06.559
You jerk!

00:24:07.799 --> 00:24:08.440
What the heck are you doing?

00:24:08.440 --> 00:24:09.839
Don't hold me back!

00:24:09.839 --> 00:24:10.279
What's wrong with you?

00:24:10.279 --> 00:24:10.799
Ask him!

00:24:10.799 --> 00:24:11.839
What he's done!

00:24:11.920 --> 00:24:12.640
What did I do?

00:24:12.640 --> 00:24:13.519
What's wrong with you?

00:24:13.519 --> 00:24:14.640
You tell me what's wrong with you!

00:24:14.640 --> 00:24:15.200
No, no, no.

00:24:15.200 --> 00:24:15.680
Don't hold me back!

00:24:15.680 --> 00:24:16.279
No, no, no!

00:24:16.279 --> 00:24:16.839
If you have something to say, say it.

00:24:16.839 --> 00:24:18.519
Don't hold me back, I'm going home.

00:24:22.799 --> 00:24:24.640
No, what are you doing?

00:24:24.640 --> 00:24:26.599
Which, which nerve is acting up again?

00:24:28.240 --> 00:24:29.200
Are you okay?

00:24:29.200 --> 00:24:30.079
Are you okay?

00:24:30.079 --> 00:24:30.839
Don't touch me.

00:24:33.440 --> 00:24:34.400
Are you alright?

00:24:34.400 --> 00:24:36.839
I... I have to talk to Big Brother about him, you...

00:24:38.880 --> 00:24:39.799
What's going on now?

00:24:39.799 --> 00:24:41.200
What did you just say to him?

00:24:41.880 --> 00:24:43.839
What's Second Brother doing?

00:24:53.720 --> 00:24:55.119
You, Li Lianbao!

00:25:11.599 --> 00:25:13.160
What, haven't you fought enough?

00:25:13.559 --> 00:25:14.519
Come out and talk.

00:25:14.880 --> 00:25:15.880
I'm sleeping.

00:25:16.640 --> 00:25:18.519
Didn't you want to hear me apologize?

00:25:20.519 --> 00:25:21.519
Will you apologize?

00:25:22.359 --> 00:25:23.519
I'll be waiting for you outside.

00:25:51.039 --> 00:25:51.839
Get in the car.

00:25:52.319 --> 00:25:53.279
Speak your mind.

00:25:53.799 --> 00:25:55.079
Let me treat your wound.

00:25:55.240 --> 00:25:56.039
No need.

00:25:56.680 --> 00:25:58.400
No treatment, no apology.

00:26:44.880 --> 00:26:46.680
Go on, tell me which part to break.

00:26:46.680 --> 00:26:47.319
Li Lianbao.

00:26:47.319 --> 00:26:48.480
What's wrong with you?

00:26:48.480 --> 00:26:49.559
There must be some misunderstanding.

00:26:49.759 --> 00:26:50.880
A misunderstanding, huh?

00:26:50.880 --> 00:26:52.079
A misunderstanding, you say?

00:26:54.279 --> 00:26:54.960
What is it?

00:26:59.880 --> 00:27:01.000
What's wrong? Are you okay?

00:27:03.880 --> 00:27:05.240
You stay right there, don't move!

00:27:05.240 --> 00:27:06.200
You jerk!

00:27:06.200 --> 00:27:07.039
What's gotten into you?

00:27:08.599 --> 00:27:09.559
Ma Weiguo.

00:27:09.920 --> 00:27:11.000
You're that old.

00:27:11.000 --> 00:27:12.279
Yet you target a young girl.

00:27:12.279 --> 00:27:13.599
Aren't you disgusting?

00:27:15.279 --> 00:27:16.039
Stop, stop, stop!

00:27:16.039 --> 00:27:17.839
You should have just asked me about this.

00:27:18.119 --> 00:27:19.880
There's really nothing between Jin Tong and me.

00:27:19.960 --> 00:27:21.559
It's not as complicated as you think.

00:27:21.559 --> 00:27:22.279
As for her and me...

00:27:22.279 --> 00:27:23.440
We just met abroad.

00:27:23.440 --> 00:27:24.440
In a bar.

00:27:24.440 --> 00:27:25.880
Someone took a photo of us.

00:27:26.279 --> 00:27:28.200
I felt a connection with her at the time.

00:27:28.200 --> 00:27:30.519
But after that night, I couldn't find her.

00:27:30.640 --> 00:27:31.480
That's all there was to it.

00:27:31.480 --> 00:27:33.599
I never imagined it would be so melodramatic.

00:27:33.799 --> 00:27:35.000
And she's your niece.

00:27:36.680 --> 00:27:38.759
So you came back still thinking about my niece?

00:27:38.759 --> 00:27:39.480
No.

00:27:39.599 --> 00:27:41.799
You're trying to deny everything after having your fun, is that it?

00:27:41.799 --> 00:27:43.279
I'm going to break your legs today!

00:27:43.279 --> 00:27:43.759
Calm down.

00:27:48.519 --> 00:27:49.359
Just you wait.

00:27:49.359 --> 00:27:50.720
If your back is bad, maybe don't fight.

00:27:52.440 --> 00:27:53.559
Alright, go back home.

00:27:54.720 --> 00:27:55.640
Pulling a knife, huh?

00:27:56.119 --> 00:27:58.000
Today, I'm definitely taking a piece of you!

00:27:58.559 --> 00:27:59.480
Calm down!

00:28:02.799 --> 00:28:03.680
Don't run!

00:28:24.759 --> 00:28:25.720
What's wrong, Uncle?

00:28:28.400 --> 00:28:29.480
Does this look familiar?

00:28:31.240 --> 00:28:32.799
If anyone crosses me...

00:28:32.799 --> 00:28:34.559
...don't blame me for going too far.

00:28:37.000 --> 00:28:38.519
You went to confront him?

00:28:38.640 --> 00:28:39.720
I didn't break his arms.

00:28:39.720 --> 00:28:40.920
I regret it now.

00:28:42.359 --> 00:28:43.240
Wait, what?

00:28:43.319 --> 00:28:44.720
Why did you use a knife?

00:28:44.720 --> 00:28:46.960
That's so dangerous! You didn't hurt him, did you?

00:28:47.599 --> 00:28:49.039
Do you think I'm stupid?

00:28:49.920 --> 00:28:52.240
If there was real blood, there'd be a lawsuit.

00:28:52.599 --> 00:28:54.319
I just ruined this piece of his clothing.

00:28:56.160 --> 00:28:57.119
No, Uncle...

00:28:57.480 --> 00:28:59.359
Now that you've done this, how awkward is it for me?

00:28:59.359 --> 00:29:00.559
How can I face him now?

00:29:00.799 --> 00:29:02.839
There was nothing going on between us.

00:29:03.400 --> 00:29:05.000
You call that nothing?

00:29:05.240 --> 00:29:07.279
An uncle and niece were hugging and kissing!

00:29:07.279 --> 00:29:08.680
That shameless...

00:29:08.680 --> 00:29:10.200
I have to teach him a lesson.

00:29:11.079 --> 00:29:12.680
And you, what's wrong with you?

00:29:13.079 --> 00:29:15.160
A few years abroad and you play so wild?

00:29:15.359 --> 00:29:17.359
Of all people, why did it have to be him?

00:29:17.359 --> 00:29:19.519
Uncle, you're exaggerating a bit.

00:29:19.599 --> 00:29:21.039
Besides, I didn't know before...

00:29:21.039 --> 00:29:22.160
...that you two had this kind of relationship.

00:29:22.160 --> 00:29:23.839
Couldn't you have found out beforehand?

00:29:23.839 --> 00:29:25.160
Where was I supposed to find out?

00:29:25.160 --> 00:29:26.200
If I had found out beforehand...

00:29:27.240 --> 00:29:28.839
Learning to talk back, are you?

00:29:29.279 --> 00:29:31.039
I... I just don't understand.

00:29:31.559 --> 00:29:34.240
You two live back-to-back in the same alley.

00:29:34.440 --> 00:29:35.319
What are you planning?

00:29:35.319 --> 00:29:36.440
To rekindle an old flame?

00:29:36.559 --> 00:29:37.599
No.

00:29:38.279 --> 00:29:40.400
Do you remember that time I came home for batteries?

00:29:40.400 --> 00:29:42.160
You were there, and Uncle Wang was too.

00:29:42.319 --> 00:29:44.039
That was the first time I met him.

00:29:46.240 --> 00:29:47.839
I'd forgotten if you hadn't mentioned it.

00:29:48.200 --> 00:29:50.200
That day, I could tell something was off with you two.

00:29:50.880 --> 00:29:52.640
Is that bastard still after you?

00:29:52.799 --> 00:29:54.359
Nothing like that.

00:29:54.359 --> 00:29:55.920
Nothing's even started yet.

00:29:55.920 --> 00:29:57.680
And after I came back, I told him.

00:29:57.680 --> 00:29:59.240
I said to leave the past in the past.

00:29:59.440 --> 00:30:00.680
So you just listen to him?

00:30:01.799 --> 00:30:02.759
Tongtong, listen to me.

00:30:03.480 --> 00:30:04.720
Move out of here immediately.

00:30:05.079 --> 00:30:06.119
Stay far away from him.

00:30:06.440 --> 00:30:07.680
You can stay in either of my apartments,
the one inside the Third Ring or the Fifth Ring.

00:30:07.680 --> 00:30:08.400
Whichever you like.

00:30:08.400 --> 00:30:09.440
You absolutely cannot stay here.

00:30:09.440 --> 00:30:10.480
That won't do.

00:30:10.720 --> 00:30:11.440
I told you.

00:30:11.440 --> 00:30:12.799
I still have to prepare my photography exhibition.

00:30:13.119 --> 00:30:14.880
Do you believe I'll call your mom right now?

00:30:14.880 --> 00:30:16.359
Uncle, you know perfectly well...

00:30:16.359 --> 00:30:18.559
...how important this exhibition is to me.

00:30:23.359 --> 00:30:24.200
How about this?

00:30:24.200 --> 00:30:25.359
If he makes...

00:30:25.359 --> 00:30:26.480
...any move on me...

00:30:26.480 --> 00:30:27.680
I'll tell you immediately.

00:30:27.680 --> 00:30:29.559
You can beat him up right then, okay?

00:30:33.079 --> 00:30:35.400
Please, Uncle.

00:30:36.079 --> 00:30:37.240
Uncle.

00:30:37.480 --> 00:30:38.119
Uncle.

00:30:38.359 --> 00:30:40.039
Just until the exhibition is over.

00:30:40.039 --> 00:30:41.039
Okay, fine.

00:30:41.759 --> 00:30:44.160
During that time, you'd better stay away from him.

00:30:44.319 --> 00:30:45.480
I'll be watching you the whole time.

00:30:46.279 --> 00:30:47.799
But when I'm working on my exhibition...

00:30:47.799 --> 00:30:48.759
...there's no discussion.

00:30:51.119 --> 00:30:53.160
Fine. We'll have nothing to do with each other.

00:30:53.160 --> 00:30:54.039
Satisfied?

00:31:07.119 --> 00:31:07.880
Yes, master.

00:31:07.960 --> 00:31:09.359
Put it right against the wall.

00:31:09.960 --> 00:31:10.720
Take it easy.

00:31:12.039 --> 00:31:12.680
Right.

00:31:13.599 --> 00:31:14.880
Here, master, put it here.

00:31:15.599 --> 00:31:16.559
Help me put these two pots...

00:31:16.559 --> 00:31:17.640
...by the window.

00:31:17.640 --> 00:31:18.400
Got it, master.

00:31:18.559 --> 00:31:19.279
Auntie Tong.

00:31:19.279 --> 00:31:22.039
Weiguo, it's right that you moved back.

00:31:22.039 --> 00:31:24.480
If you go abroad again in the future,

00:31:24.480 --> 00:31:25.960
I'll keep this house for you.

00:31:25.960 --> 00:31:26.680
Don't you worry.

00:31:26.680 --> 00:31:27.720
Sorry for the trouble.

00:31:28.000 --> 00:31:29.759
Kid.

00:31:30.079 --> 00:31:30.799
Uncle Tong.

00:31:30.960 --> 00:31:32.039
Look at this.

00:31:32.720 --> 00:31:34.839
Look at all your old stuff.

00:31:34.839 --> 00:31:35.440
What stuff?

00:31:35.440 --> 00:31:36.960
Qiu'er kept it all for you.

00:31:39.079 --> 00:31:40.960
Look, look, what a mess.

00:31:40.960 --> 00:31:41.720
Quick, quick.

00:31:42.839 --> 00:31:43.240
Come on, come on.

00:31:43.240 --> 00:31:44.759
These are all things I collected as a kid.

00:31:44.759 --> 00:31:46.160
Just throw away what's useless.

00:31:46.160 --> 00:31:47.480
Oh, don't do that!

00:31:47.480 --> 00:31:49.519
I'll keep it, I'll take it all.

00:31:50.160 --> 00:31:52.279
Your uncle just loves picking up junk.

00:31:52.880 --> 00:31:54.279
She doesn't get it, she doesn't.

00:31:54.279 --> 00:31:55.240
What do you mean I don't get it?

00:31:55.240 --> 00:31:56.000
Only you understand.

00:31:56.000 --> 00:31:57.599
It's piled up under the bed.

00:31:57.599 --> 00:31:58.640
What's the big deal? What's the big deal?

00:31:58.640 --> 00:32:00.200
That's the memory of an era.

00:32:00.200 --> 00:32:01.759
What era memory?

00:32:01.759 --> 00:32:03.400
It's not food or drink.

00:32:03.400 --> 00:32:04.599
Lighting a fire for the stove...

00:32:04.599 --> 00:32:06.359
...wouldn't even boil a kettle.

00:32:06.359 --> 00:32:07.960
What's the point of telling you this?

00:32:07.960 --> 00:32:09.519
You don't understand.

00:32:09.519 --> 00:32:11.240
Who understands like you do, you old man.

00:32:11.240 --> 00:32:11.960
It's fine, it's fine.

00:32:12.240 --> 00:32:12.839
By the way.

00:32:13.119 --> 00:32:14.319
This room...

00:32:14.400 --> 00:32:16.400
...I think it's a bit damp.

00:32:16.400 --> 00:32:18.279
You should find a renovation master...

00:32:18.279 --> 00:32:19.519
...to help you fix it up.

00:32:19.519 --> 00:32:20.960
Otherwise, it's not livable.

00:32:21.279 --> 00:32:22.000
Auntie Tong.

00:32:22.079 --> 00:32:23.400
I don't plan for anyone to live here.

00:32:24.160 --> 00:32:25.359
Not live here?

00:32:25.359 --> 00:32:26.359
Then what for?

00:32:26.359 --> 00:32:27.680
I'm going to convert it into a toilet.

00:32:27.680 --> 00:32:28.960
Convert it into a toilet?

00:32:29.160 --> 00:32:31.160
I've researched it long ago.

00:32:31.160 --> 00:32:32.799
High-tech and eco-friendly.

00:32:32.799 --> 00:32:35.960
Electric blade shreds it, goes down the drain.

00:32:35.960 --> 00:32:37.640
You're everywhere, this old man.

00:32:37.640 --> 00:32:38.279
It's fine, it's fine.

00:32:38.279 --> 00:32:38.559
Really.

00:32:38.559 --> 00:32:39.359
Auntie Tong, you go rest.

00:32:39.359 --> 00:32:39.759
Okay.

00:32:39.759 --> 00:32:41.079
Come on, go rest a bit.

00:32:41.200 --> 00:32:41.720
Okay.

00:32:43.599 --> 00:32:44.880
Come on, come on, master, here.

00:32:44.880 --> 00:32:45.519
Alright, okay.

00:32:45.519 --> 00:32:46.599
Here, easy, easy, easy.

00:32:46.720 --> 00:32:47.279
Come on, come on.

00:32:47.279 --> 00:32:48.240
Weiguo.

00:32:48.799 --> 00:32:52.319
Your uncle won't take your stuff for free, you...

00:32:53.559 --> 00:32:55.799
...how is this like Sun Wukong?

00:32:55.799 --> 00:32:58.559
This... and a bunch of little monkey kings next to it.

00:32:59.680 --> 00:33:02.599
You're exactly like your dad when he was young.

00:33:02.599 --> 00:33:05.640
Your head's full of strange ideas.

00:33:06.359 --> 00:33:07.039
This.

00:33:09.559 --> 00:33:12.839
This here is a letter your dad wrote to me.

00:33:12.839 --> 00:33:14.359
Treasure it well.

00:33:14.640 --> 00:33:16.480
These two notebooks are my records...

00:33:16.480 --> 00:33:18.680
...of some stories from our alley.

00:33:18.920 --> 00:33:19.799
Here, look.

00:33:20.519 --> 00:33:21.440
Originally,

00:33:21.440 --> 00:33:24.839
I wanted to train Qiu'er as my successor.

00:33:25.039 --> 00:33:28.039
Now it seems he's not cut out for it, is he?

00:33:28.480 --> 00:33:30.599
Back when you went abroad, you were young.

00:33:30.599 --> 00:33:32.839
Now it seems just right.

00:33:33.839 --> 00:33:35.279
Thank you, Uncle Tong. I'll keep them.

00:33:35.279 --> 00:33:36.599
You're welcome.

00:33:36.839 --> 00:33:37.519
See.

00:33:41.079 --> 00:33:42.000
Brother Daxi

00:33:42.119 --> 00:33:43.359
Give my regards to your family

00:33:44.000 --> 00:33:45.680
The past few days of travel were exhausting

00:33:45.680 --> 00:33:47.240
Only today have I settled down

00:33:47.720 --> 00:33:48.960
Though I have no time to reply

00:33:49.240 --> 00:33:50.559
I miss you dearly

00:33:51.200 --> 00:33:53.839
It's been a week since I was transferred to Shanghai for training

00:33:54.480 --> 00:33:55.599
Now past thirty

00:33:55.920 --> 00:33:57.880
I can't help but lament my ability to learn

00:33:57.880 --> 00:33:59.400
It's truly not what it used to be

00:34:00.119 --> 00:34:03.480
Thinking about working and living abroad in the future

00:34:03.720 --> 00:34:05.519
I can't help but feel some panic in my heart

00:34:05.799 --> 00:34:07.319
And even more reluctance

00:34:07.960 --> 00:34:09.559
Yesterday by the Huangpu River

00:34:09.800 --> 00:34:11.800
Looking at the lush greenery on the opposite bank

00:34:11.800 --> 00:34:13.760
Sparsely dotted with construction sites

00:34:13.840 --> 00:34:15.599
I wonder, when I revisit this place

00:34:15.960 --> 00:34:17.840
What will it look like then?

00:34:18.440 --> 00:34:19.280
I guess

00:34:19.480 --> 00:34:21.079
Probably everywhere will be filled with

00:34:21.079 --> 00:34:22.559
Five or six-story tall buildings

00:34:23.480 --> 00:34:24.360
Elder Brother

00:34:24.760 --> 00:34:26.079
These two banks of the river

00:34:26.079 --> 00:34:27.599
Seem like our two generations

00:34:27.840 --> 00:34:29.239
Hardship on this side

00:34:29.480 --> 00:34:31.280
The future on that side

00:34:32.039 --> 00:34:33.000
Tell me

00:34:33.440 --> 00:34:35.119
When the children grow up

00:34:35.320 --> 00:34:36.679
What will these letters between them

00:34:37.159 --> 00:34:38.639
Talk about then?

00:34:39.719 --> 00:34:40.960
I'll stop here for now

00:34:41.400 --> 00:34:43.440
There's work to be done at hand again

00:34:43.719 --> 00:34:45.880
I'll write to you slowly later

00:34:46.800 --> 00:34:48.119
Short letter, deep affection

00:34:48.719 --> 00:34:49.960
Wishing you all the best

00:34:50.280 --> 00:34:51.760
Your younger brother, Zhiyuan

00:34:52.079 --> 00:34:54.519
April 10, 1986

00:34:55.360 --> 00:34:56.400
Third Uncle

00:34:57.639 --> 00:34:58.400
Third Uncle

00:34:59.360 --> 00:35:00.880
Come in, the door's unlocked

00:35:02.400 --> 00:35:03.199
Third Uncle

00:35:03.440 --> 00:35:05.320
How come you're not worried at all?

00:35:05.320 --> 00:35:06.480
I've been waiting for you

00:35:06.480 --> 00:35:07.800
To give me the second treatment

00:35:07.800 --> 00:35:09.199
You haven't forgotten about me, have you?

00:35:09.719 --> 00:35:10.800
Don't be in such a hurry

00:35:10.800 --> 00:35:11.960
Your illness has deep roots

00:35:11.960 --> 00:35:13.360
I need to think it over carefully

00:35:14.119 --> 00:35:14.639
Alright

00:35:15.239 --> 00:35:16.199
However

00:35:16.760 --> 00:35:18.559
I now have a preliminary idea

00:35:19.440 --> 00:35:21.519
So how do you plan to treat me?

00:35:22.039 --> 00:35:23.719
It's not that spending money thing again, is it?

00:35:23.840 --> 00:35:24.519
To be honest

00:35:24.679 --> 00:35:27.519
Spending money felt great at first

00:35:27.639 --> 00:35:28.960
But later on, the more I spent

00:35:28.960 --> 00:35:30.000
The less fun it became

00:35:30.519 --> 00:35:31.280
Don't worry

00:35:31.280 --> 00:35:32.960
I'll definitely give you a big surprise

00:35:32.960 --> 00:35:33.800
Once I've figured it out

00:35:33.800 --> 00:35:34.719
I'll tell you

00:35:35.000 --> 00:35:35.639
Okay then

00:35:35.840 --> 00:35:37.519
I'll wait for your news

00:35:37.800 --> 00:35:38.679
You should rest early

00:35:38.679 --> 00:35:39.480
I'll head back now

00:35:41.599 --> 00:35:43.039
What have your dad and the others been up to lately?

00:35:43.599 --> 00:35:44.280
My dad?

00:35:45.519 --> 00:35:46.960
You don't know yet, right?

00:35:47.280 --> 00:35:48.239
It's Second Uncle

00:35:48.239 --> 00:35:49.559
He's been egging my dad on

00:35:49.559 --> 00:35:51.360
To use Penglexuan to start a business together

00:35:53.880 --> 00:35:54.960
He really knows how to dream

00:35:56.159 --> 00:35:58.239
But my dad shot him down

00:35:58.480 --> 00:36:00.159
With my dad being so lazy

00:36:00.159 --> 00:36:01.559
He simply can't be bothered to go through the hassle

00:36:03.000 --> 00:36:04.119
That Second Uncle of yours

00:36:04.119 --> 00:36:05.239
Has no good points

00:36:05.239 --> 00:36:06.199
Except for one thing

00:36:06.400 --> 00:36:07.679
Once he sets his mind on something

00:36:07.679 --> 00:36:08.960
He absolutely will not give up

00:36:08.960 --> 00:36:10.000
He'll keep pestering your dad

00:36:10.320 --> 00:36:10.920
Yeah

00:36:15.679 --> 00:36:17.920
This new wine in the shop is good. Try it.

00:36:19.440 --> 00:36:20.480
You're really giving it to me?

00:36:23.000 --> 00:36:23.719
I'll try it.

00:36:25.599 --> 00:36:27.400
You'll try it just because I told you to?

00:36:27.559 --> 00:36:28.760
What did the doctor say?

00:36:28.760 --> 00:36:30.159
Do you even want to get better?

00:36:30.159 --> 00:36:32.199
Aren't you being ridiculous?

00:36:32.199 --> 00:36:33.760
If you want to drink it yourself, then drink it yourself.

00:36:33.760 --> 00:36:35.239
You're so bored you're teasing me.

00:36:35.360 --> 00:36:36.880
I'm testing you.

00:36:36.880 --> 00:36:37.800
Annoying.

00:36:40.239 --> 00:36:43.320
Weiguo even took leave and stayed for our Feifei.

00:36:43.320 --> 00:36:44.039
That's why I say...

00:36:44.039 --> 00:36:46.119
You can only rely on your own brothers.

00:36:47.320 --> 00:36:48.239
It shows...

00:36:49.760 --> 00:36:51.559
He still has me, his big brother, in his heart.

00:36:51.559 --> 00:36:52.840
Oh, come off it.

00:36:53.119 --> 00:36:54.480
A toad on the main road...

00:36:54.480 --> 00:36:56.039
Pretending to be a colorful little jeep.

00:36:56.599 --> 00:36:58.159
Stop with all that sour, grumbling talk.

00:37:00.760 --> 00:37:02.199
Why isn't Feifei up yet? Feifei!

00:37:02.199 --> 00:37:02.880
Feifei!

00:37:04.880 --> 00:37:06.559
Feifei! Dinner's ready!

00:37:07.800 --> 00:37:09.480
Can he even hear us from here?

00:37:09.840 --> 00:37:10.760
My voice is loud.

00:37:13.119 --> 00:37:13.920
Finished your homework?

00:37:13.920 --> 00:37:14.920
Homework's done.

00:37:17.280 --> 00:37:19.000
I'm telling you, you're not allowed to drink.

00:37:19.000 --> 00:37:19.920
I won't drink.

00:37:20.480 --> 00:37:21.800
Then who are you pouring it for?

00:37:22.480 --> 00:37:23.519
Alright, alright.

00:37:24.159 --> 00:37:25.679
What? You're just pouring it for your dad?

00:37:25.679 --> 00:37:27.039
Mom, it's fine.

00:37:27.039 --> 00:37:28.599
Dad will just take a tiny sip, right?

00:37:28.599 --> 00:37:30.360
What tiny sip? You...

00:37:30.480 --> 00:37:31.960
What's this? Need a favor from me?

00:37:32.599 --> 00:37:33.480
No.

00:37:34.440 --> 00:37:35.360
Well...

00:37:36.119 --> 00:37:37.760
Third Uncle told me...

00:37:38.360 --> 00:37:39.960
That from now on, I'll learn from him.

00:37:39.960 --> 00:37:41.159
I have to listen to him in everything.

00:37:41.320 --> 00:37:43.440
I have to do whatever he tells me to do.

00:37:43.679 --> 00:37:46.519
He said you and Mom can't interfere either.

00:37:49.559 --> 00:37:50.880
He really said that?

00:37:51.119 --> 00:37:51.800
Yeah.

00:37:55.519 --> 00:37:58.599
Fine. Trust is the most important thing.

00:37:58.880 --> 00:37:59.239
Right.

00:37:59.239 --> 00:38:00.320
As long as you promise...

00:38:01.280 --> 00:38:02.360
To take the college entrance exam.

00:38:03.000 --> 00:38:04.000
And study hard.

00:38:04.320 --> 00:38:06.599
Then we'll give him our full trust.

00:38:07.559 --> 00:38:10.320
Okay. Since Third Uncle said so...

00:38:10.320 --> 00:38:12.000
You don't need to manage me anymore, right?

00:38:12.000 --> 00:38:13.280
What do you mean I don't need to manage you?

00:38:13.280 --> 00:38:14.840
I'm your dad. If I don't manage you...

00:38:15.800 --> 00:38:17.480
Would you have grown up this big?

00:38:17.639 --> 00:38:18.199
Let me tell you...

00:38:18.199 --> 00:38:20.599
His is a foreign system.

00:38:21.519 --> 00:38:24.639
Mine is a traditional Chinese cultural system.

00:38:24.639 --> 00:38:26.519
We'll give you a Chinese-Western fusion.

00:38:30.920 --> 00:38:31.440
I'm going.

00:38:31.559 --> 00:38:33.039
Son, serve the rice.

00:38:33.039 --> 00:38:33.679
Going to study.

00:38:33.679 --> 00:38:34.800
I ate a small burger this afternoon.

00:38:34.800 --> 00:38:35.840
I'm okay. You guys eat.

00:38:36.840 --> 00:38:38.119
Good. He knows to study now.

00:38:38.119 --> 00:38:39.079
Isn't that right?

00:38:40.679 --> 00:38:42.599
Second Brother said he's coming to see you tomorrow.

00:38:44.599 --> 00:38:46.480
Aren't you and Qianqian discussing a partnership?

00:38:46.480 --> 00:38:48.199
He heard a rumor from somewhere.

00:38:48.199 --> 00:38:49.400
Said he's coming to keep an eye on you.

00:38:50.719 --> 00:38:51.880
Why keep an eye on me?

00:38:51.880 --> 00:38:53.239
Would Qianqian harm me?

00:38:56.119 --> 00:38:57.159
Tell me...

00:38:57.920 --> 00:39:01.239
Could Second Brother and Qianqian get together?

00:39:02.360 --> 00:39:03.360
Those two...

00:39:03.360 --> 00:39:04.440
Look, today you argue with me.

00:39:04.440 --> 00:39:05.360
Tomorrow I argue with you.

00:39:05.360 --> 00:39:07.559
That's how they do it in TV dramas.

00:39:07.559 --> 00:39:08.199
These two people...

00:39:08.199 --> 00:39:09.760
They argue and argue and end up together.

00:39:09.760 --> 00:39:11.239
TV dramas are made up.

00:39:13.360 --> 00:39:15.079
But if they do get together...

00:39:15.519 --> 00:39:16.559
It would actually be pretty good.

00:39:16.559 --> 00:39:17.199
Think about it.

00:39:18.000 --> 00:39:19.599
Qianqian has a son.

00:39:19.599 --> 00:39:20.800
Lianbao has a daughter.

00:39:21.079 --> 00:39:22.119
If those two get together...

00:39:22.119 --> 00:39:23.039
It makes the character for "good."

00:39:23.119 --> 00:39:24.440
Right, a son and a daughter.

00:39:24.440 --> 00:39:25.079
Exactly.

00:39:30.280 --> 00:39:32.119
I'll just dip the very tip of my chopstick.

00:39:39.800 --> 00:39:41.480
This wine is so fragrant.

00:39:41.480 --> 00:39:42.760
Seriously, aren't you something.

00:39:42.760 --> 00:39:44.639
You keep tempting me with it.

00:39:46.719 --> 00:39:47.599
Where are you going?

00:39:47.880 --> 00:39:48.920
I'm going to eat over there.

00:39:48.920 --> 00:39:50.079
You think if you go over there...

00:39:50.079 --> 00:39:51.960
You won't crave this wine anymore?

00:39:52.679 --> 00:39:53.519
Wang Chunsheng.

00:39:54.840 --> 00:39:56.000
Wang Chunsheng.

00:39:58.199 --> 00:39:59.840
This wine is really fragrant.

00:40:13.519 --> 00:40:15.159
Last time, I had you two

00:40:15.159 --> 00:40:17.440
help me give feedback on the script.

00:40:17.440 --> 00:40:19.360
The effect was fantastic.

00:40:19.360 --> 00:40:21.679
The Beijing dialect was spot on.

00:40:22.159 --> 00:40:23.800
Oh, right. Take a look.

00:40:23.800 --> 00:40:27.039
This is my creative output from the last couple of days.

00:40:27.039 --> 00:40:27.920
Take a look.

00:40:29.840 --> 00:40:31.039
Look, look.

00:40:31.719 --> 00:40:32.800
As for me,

00:40:32.800 --> 00:40:36.159
I'd also like to invite you two to accompany me to a meeting.

00:40:37.079 --> 00:40:37.760
A meeting?

00:40:37.760 --> 00:40:38.559
Yes.

00:40:38.920 --> 00:40:41.280
I've arranged to meet with a top person from a platform.

00:40:41.280 --> 00:40:42.639
This guy,

00:40:42.840 --> 00:40:44.760
don't let his young age fool you.

00:40:44.760 --> 00:40:47.159
He's an absolute fox, a real operator.

00:40:47.440 --> 00:40:49.519
He'd squeeze blood from a stone.

00:40:49.519 --> 00:40:52.199
We need to knock his arrogance down a peg.

00:40:52.400 --> 00:40:53.239
Otherwise,

00:40:53.239 --> 00:40:54.920
the price for my script

00:40:54.920 --> 00:40:56.639
will be driven way down by him.

00:40:57.119 --> 00:40:59.320
Grandpa Tong, you mean...

00:41:00.360 --> 00:41:01.320
My meaning is,

00:41:01.320 --> 00:41:04.559
I'm asking you two to do me a favor.

00:41:04.559 --> 00:41:06.000
Accompany me in putting on a show.

00:41:06.000 --> 00:41:09.320
Let them see how impressive I am with two assistants.

00:41:10.119 --> 00:41:11.760
I've even thought of the division of labor.

00:41:11.920 --> 00:41:13.840
You handle business, okay?

00:41:14.039 --> 00:41:16.440
At the meeting, you keep making calls.

00:41:16.920 --> 00:41:19.440
You say, "Teacher Daxi

00:41:20.079 --> 00:41:21.280
is very busy lately.

00:41:21.280 --> 00:41:22.719
His schedule is completely full.

00:41:22.719 --> 00:41:25.280
Booked solid until the end of next year."

00:41:26.119 --> 00:41:26.880
As for you,

00:41:26.880 --> 00:41:28.320
you handle lifestyle, right?

00:41:28.320 --> 00:41:29.480
You just keep

00:41:29.559 --> 00:41:31.199
handing me this thermos cup.

00:41:31.199 --> 00:41:32.159
You tell him,

00:41:32.159 --> 00:41:34.000
"This was a gift from President Ma.

00:41:34.000 --> 00:41:36.280
Old mountain ginseng from Changbai Mountain.

00:41:36.559 --> 00:41:39.440
And he has to drink it daily, and while it's hot."

00:41:40.480 --> 00:41:42.440
Hold on, Uncle Tong.

00:41:42.960 --> 00:41:44.440
These are all old tricks.

00:41:44.440 --> 00:41:45.679
If your thinking

00:41:45.679 --> 00:41:47.280
is still stuck twenty years in the past,

00:41:47.280 --> 00:41:48.719
it'll be hard for you to keep writing.

00:41:51.000 --> 00:41:52.760
What do you mean by that?

00:41:54.360 --> 00:41:55.880
Uncle Ma's words are truly

00:41:56.119 --> 00:41:57.679
equally unpleasant to everyone.

00:41:57.679 --> 00:41:59.039
I'm just telling the truth.

00:42:00.840 --> 00:42:01.960
It's okay, Grandpa Tong.

00:42:01.960 --> 00:42:02.800
I, alone,

00:42:02.800 --> 00:42:04.159
can do the work of two people.

00:42:04.679 --> 00:42:05.760
You're still the best.

00:42:06.039 --> 00:42:08.039
So it's settled, okay?

00:42:08.039 --> 00:42:09.800
Okay, no problem. Good.

00:42:09.960 --> 00:42:11.000
Good.